        <item>
            <title>【评测】Honor Magic7 Pro 深圳发布快速评测，机身手感更佳 + 荧幕更护眼 + 长焦镜再强化 + 鹰眼终可连拍 + 更多实用 AI 功能现场速试</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/01/honor-magic7pro-shenzen-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honor-magic7pro-shenzen-review</link>
